a/sc/QfUfj_ak5ia5VNEFd0sRhNMg-27WMtlNwHaXRypbWrG_2Zra8QPHMkUYVqT39i9wrTLTPvLlySPLkMbB5brr5mTXXb74wz3V4ZsxECTozcacvF_ZC61tKpblEZQT1q9qr9XfzdGs6hw79Yw4NTnYE7QQ6el_Z2xCRxetPl8-I2gOtmdV9QFcekd9b877QPT2oRLT7J5pdklZRSMdn3jX8OX_SOTx75YCzMy2gkch0CiJbkKWQhn5g41qIlymInaB8sAuHd3wrsz0Ajf7YhZQcy-5ODrkd5xGBzKHLtTxV9nM3Ul1FmMhHDalXWOI3voDO6XCoBV3iylY_NX8QVLDTA5oABC-DfB09C7958sYrn2-PW5y-aOK2vi6mpzX6Sxg5uhTm8S-FAJ9t9AzMxEreC1m-EqvHsniObX7hr4C30M0kcOlOv0rq0sKyw3AkIsisQ1XsJ4589NYIfdWEhuZONvS7z8M5yQDBiu_Eec0zL_pz6BnStQjycDw75hF4r4s_riOp2U/pKOuCW1LOG3SXLx6rbyMJ4OAPGpOcr7Y/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="最高法院表示选举日投票截止日期存在分歧"&gt;该案可能对提前投票产生的影响&lt;/a&gt;表示担忧。在周一持续两个多小时的听证会上，法院讨论了密西西比州的一项法律，该法律允许邮寄选票只要在选举日后五个工作日内送达即可被计入。共和党人称这项措施不符合联邦法律，推翻这项措施的裁决将颠覆多达 29 个州的类似宽限期。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/vFOKR8MmeAYstDbVs3aL-2tAHmb3FZ_x9rDl1YEvN6qHo8dm_I1taFk-SbYHawL8CY7WRGAFsESapgl1lQQ2E_e1f4k9JOpxtrglWOp0dA0ewPPYAKB3R59pLA2438jt6sppxLq_k703kD8604V-Nd2EF0cNulNIXoi5eLzuIhcvMth2SYsKEzw55-qADsjvyG9Fdjb9d9PCUFyi4ED5K1um3kelu37fNumEtVgyZo5AnMWpwbqJ-n5U8BHV7PZUtXzMe7drk_cRbxzvaTLAVOLrIMnsicw0ZrHVyXxt0bes-ZLqilVnxbiHOdg5HW0OYb-_Ge5PMFzqrE0gq3EQlIREhKdyV87niPeJxZQuMKdy6XbDLjHh4lrNoYzw6PmJbmRVdlCSTn62ZNz7-olG/XBkczkuglHstWmp19aXTfV4_goR9QQ6k/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOdgAzSE7LAI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iOdgAzSE7LAI/v3/pidjEfPlU1QWZop3vfGKsrX.ke8XuWirGYh1PKgEw44kE/-1x-1.png" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&gt; &lt;/figure