&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;29 年前：&lt;/strong&gt;在中国互联网发展初期，《&lt;em style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;连线》杂志的&lt;/em&gt;一篇文章创造了“防火墙”一词，预示着国家控制系统的出现。如今，创新与约束之间的同样平衡&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/sh7IU8G1JYxUkR3mudMifpbeW1jFx6emJyDmqGPP-Y2eWTmv00A43KRENF3MN-THEMSXCm70Xwo14-sAHX_Yk_nFG8uR3e0FkDJcK9xgy6ZGp7Np5p5l1B_ZhRzO4vDLakQM6gVHUzbFG4tfVO2vLwLcgcVx6VZ5RoFyt1fmEN50Sk5Roe7xgMVrVCE5-5YWrQPYlYZLkmRFM9ELHofcqtyftrKTNAi6r-Pp6KccG49CPc_GpB0fEXRtT9VjSTN61JReKcs0LRj3iOlynhOv4qZeyOrpk9_aHu8cZhhrF0kixwqSGNVFk1QscpUk8AtLelbZjNni501JZ5SR_J5uNI0TM3ppynxVltizS01nMcOhYi2jhV6r4b9xj_1BczgUIUyHPJptAW8QA5vyJwRLt8b-E5tpjhUyvNvjVWa6BINW6g-6n1t7SKyufdOZF5KHoayfNMJ6McqKuZOh1xO7Q7Yrb1XekYnEmQ2epPnVGEuCymN2U7Ywwi2vdwRMFy3cvYEoOSSew5BLawIc6AdhNw/g9FArpt779640IZcrj2edM8wVn7EjDwr/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="中国的防火墙揭示了人工智能的未来"&gt;正在塑造中国的人工智能&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt; &lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;60 年前：&lt;/strong&gt; 1966 年世界杯前几天，足球界最珍贵的奖杯消失了，一周后才被一只名叫 Pickles 的狗发现。这个混乱的传奇故事实际上&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/Lpi32yJ3EVaKXqkfMLPr41PgwEfDC3Qr9hdjLneWGjUKhBm2nN5BJy9QuCvzrGi899hu26s4phgGY_h6CQswIH3Z2R4prbnQ1s7dxZJdQQ9JB6AhNxfg16ol_068d30JuTXHBc4quMNYjYWXwzklXhzJ2XfHWIbbrxZnhipYEUswQ6Fh6nokfXAORP3Hjzw1SV4BogS2X5zS3QgTFNg1qOu80tIllvwRcQ4Fy7rZaHUTWDvfDUTDW7UvCNW1xNVPvHsS7pxJI6oOzT_GNKes_wdxhbRnhRymI-G10r0XtlCrQW9LcXoLJoTnJD3exIDUNgaNZc2Kxoqn3tkJzyjx-PdrxSMhLOCD-9fBUzm_A1fx9bf7l6yTDYcKu2OkMNDNWON6ClKikB1FhzT2dvlGCQrXDkwt1ojs3VIDoeiFRGJ2KWD5rsIjFd1Q_YXsIzPWGc6IrU7iFVOraFQusC0QmPoS2wi9OPQI2ekCkS2hTXLrd7KX7ALwBv7ZvhdOstxsCGXojmuX45PmCV-md2FFoAVih_D9zNcmqNdE/vMPo_s0l7w6reEbWqZnSB1iRdQAlYBKl/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="世界杯失踪的混乱一周"&gt;比其整洁的结局所暗示的还要奇怪&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;strong style="font-size: 16px;"&gt;近 200 年前：&lt;/strong&gt;当工业革命袭击英国时，小说家将其剧变转化为有关工作、阶级和社会变革的故事。他们所捕捉到的&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/g-hGThouayyBTeWabFi6hRWu5tTlgyRoilsHghH-kIpuXAD0itJhiKa2kjw4sb2BE6N2m3fF7tT5g2o9ypolBDy_fLxmpcL9qWQcRgHLaB68joil3bi6BHpo6UPNMj3FyJ7LzZI6942f3fb_H26TvYYxeVi3eBmljomDHxsSIhIE5CZk9oNJNwttmehx-K6x_Y9X1-07XaRhzGDp3Ipng0sRozFNjvxvRrE9salGYBDu5FE5BY7CMJH9z1k44v_q3IFSZJzu1QsQFjlZDJTy26oeJ7iYilRpc2YpaAmSuOROVBCbHU4RlLNpWSOLZ3L16fQ98I97X-8nSg1hyWjQIr9usEq_blIFtBzS7he7om6WZ20NTSyD5UN0M36mlUJQ2gSFlqqDmIgfcdH_gpJOLWEYDOTZuutRJIcjT-tJ_mu30hBhou6Vhl_ZHKsfDaR5ZgVsF8uCg5YSLlDp39irh64OM17Go3d_48tCbtVpv3fvjmSdFs0CSoVxgzg7K8kj9jtmDrkPTR4porA1f_KmELvaOR4vwcG1Pa1MJQ/C_jHsqsWLct9C8Ckz-8CP4SZcXbLgFBV/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank" title="人工智能革命的最佳指南可能是维多利亚时代的小说"&gt;可能是我们现在对人工智能革命最接近的指南&lt;/a&gt;。&lt;/p&gt;&lt;figure style="margin: 20px 0;"&gt; &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/YoPRMKAIDk37UVDkAWzromIiRQ1d8ZZbG0fDJe_6eSPDZKwRyaPQVynqLIX6EfrOkCz4sbwbrJfjJUtptZyNgBhRcSWmCfZWaAZGBwVJcVtIoedg0IXkYgljRqaKhZXCGeIdka-csa5MH_DSvxdXtzMGju62KEF0hJRY20Px2TM39iUEpanJPoAxbSmmpXrCxpNa2fKqu05spi6d93CbUtzOnJpI4-RnpxUdpTxC_PSl6stl3A2Sq7xoVrzu371kiT7ldKBWIT20Vf7gW2KVOuMfDznSeRjo_2ZOMOiKtj279MqAS7SVxQGYaWm50_c8Ki4jDOJVd8DvxNAM1T5BvltUpMO3XISYu0EBCkwqE-yz9G3L2-GROwXLCGvuGtiEkA7TJzvSguEUu8U7H9uUeCf_f80FHVpnj8I/MJFv2HPI8Vo8Z-Eko4sxnFYXD5WOiwD9/19" style="font-size: inherit; color: #00e;" target="_blank"&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;table width="580"&gt;&lt;tr&gt;&lt;td&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izeA0Cdft83s/v0/-999x-999.gif" alt="" width="580"/&gt;&lt;/td&gt;&lt;/tr&gt;&lt;/table&gt;&lt;div style="display:none"&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;img alt="替代" src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/izeA0Cdft83s/v0/-999x-999.gif" style="width: 100%; display: block; margin-bottom: 4px;" /&gt;&lt;!--[if mso]&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;![endif]--&gt;&lt;/a&