height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;混合解决方案&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;div style="margin-top: 24px; margin-left: 8px; margin-right: 8px;"&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-size: 22px; margin: 0;"&gt; “ &lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/a/sc/ALo4oHAeKSp_pVRYVpcdvxBjmWdkOj3nXQza1bYzN_VkpSKeaZFG7EIP2Vn0B3QkegP-NCmLreZK_jetnDSwGkGcPg_L3CYoSO_9xrIrl1ZtaJ2dyd07XfVx7O4iJJNQyNjAPuaD36psl4_cvvZBJggqulojVoe3N5ceNbayEdy_BTTJhnUQ-IleqgyiBBCGs4yb4zCtXsSg4rBFHLOnSldNb1m7IjMLhJFMvbVZL75IL57as4YLs_ZNa65Zn7VXgH47ab_VsUiRss7JvgrVDS7sTHJO-_MqI4_6Djeasn5J2zvKioUr9Vy7zyuOj4xGYdCSYJ1WQRxtvxK68FCrcu96NJPfKSuTDwVzpSO1HNYE-EJqcriPrQZdHtXb9A0zjHARK6TPWcB9dxMA_JyshAH35kOCkJNc_DInzx3zeBzYmauJoUao0icwn1YbsLhoruy_7hqsGrbTZnQbjMc6JIuyYVOCEtBLkdQEiundgfOXVkn1bTeFMJSleB4Pl16X_Ww4sxzH/m2Fax5TtGzWJWrYTeT64gmrUOhIMd94l/19" rel="noopener noreferrer" style="color: #00e; font-size: inherit;" target="_blank" title="飙升的天然气价格重新点燃了电动汽车的兴趣"&gt;美国的叙述中遗漏&lt;/a&gt;的是我们每个家庭拥有两辆车的奢侈”&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-weight: 700; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;伊泰·米凯利&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; font-style: italic; font-weight: 400; margin: 0;"&gt;TD Cowen 投资银行分析师&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p style="text-align: center; line-height: 140%; margin: 8px 0 0;"&gt;在美国，拥有两辆或更多汽车的家庭可以决定他们的至少一辆汽车应该不受加油站的束缚。 &lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;h2 style="font-size: 24px; line-height: 30px; font-weight: 700; padding-top: 12px; border-top: 1px solid; margin-top: 40px;"&gt;电动卡车赌注&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p style="margin-top: 24px; font-size: 16px;"&gt;&lt;a href="https://links.message.bloomberg.com/s/c/lfNiV-RqVwHp-aKXuRzNrhq0x4DpnGKepggQ70z5_DNtGCw6kqtO92AsNyqAQ_OswOAg6-nLES50bvdsZK-1Lkhyc-enKu4x6_IL0lBlcLZ8m9TbKzQqvji6w3_3B92z5BJovBsbQcFE48ZnP17_pb9-f63S8h5Cw3vJCfaMqMUEz_tmqBKaYflQo8q9_abmQXdkXHw5Bi7eJQ6qmYlO8XzNZppJUbZUnqfXMElMkfGECCzRaOT4mKub5MQ92LeDuhHljUj0cbFNeCDu5MBDRTG89BMssJxKg4Kd39sSFCfUDNj1DTP2MmknKs1corQzVHmv/0nlqM8Wppvte6O8AJ1uh3ELBn2Rym9Zv/19" rel="noopener noreferre